&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Temples" /><category term="Gardens" /><summary type="html">The garden and Bentendo (right) behind Seiryo-ji Temple. 清涼寺の裏手にある庭園と弁天堂（右）。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2304_DSCF7952-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2304_DSCF7952-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">River Morning・川朝</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230423/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="River Morning・川朝" /><published>2023-04-23T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2023-04-23T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/boat-ride</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230423/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
A flat-bottom &lt;em&gt;Yakatabune&lt;/em&gt; boat takes visitors on a ride  along the Oi River in Arashiyama. Piloted with only a bamboo pole, it is a calm, peaceful ride.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
In the deep river gorge, the morning sun only reaches the boat, the rocks, and the maple leaves, while the far side of the river and the opposite bank are in shadow; creating a high contrast look. The boat is  translucent, so it gets illuminated by the sun as well.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
 嵐山の大堰川を、平底の屋形船で遊覧する。竹竿一本で操縦する、穏やかな船旅です。
&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    

深い渓谷の中で、朝日は船と岩ともみじにしか届かず、川の向こう側と対岸は影になり、コントラストが高い。ボートは半透明なので、太陽に照らされている。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Boats" /><summary type="html">A flat-bottom Yakatabune boat takes visitors on a ride along the Oi River in Arashiyama. Piloted with only a bamboo pole, it is a calm, peaceful ride. In the deep river gorge, the morning sun only reaches the boat, the rocks, and the maple leaves, while the far side of the river and the opposite bank are in shadow; creating a high contrast look. The boat is translucent, so it gets illuminated by the sun as well. 嵐山の大堰川を、平底の屋形船で遊覧する。竹竿一本で操縦する、穏やかな船旅です。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2304_DSCF7944-2-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2304_DSCF7944-2-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Konan Wisteria Festival・江南藤まつり</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230422/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Konan Wisteria Festival・江南藤まつり" /><published>2023-04-22T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2023-04-22T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/konan</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230422/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
